[Enter feedback here]
Hi team,

In this doc (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/virtual-machines/acu), apparently, the Dav4 and Dasv4 series do not support nested virtualization.

However, in the main page of dav4 and dasv4 series (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/virtual-machines/dav4-dasv4-series), it says nested virtualization is supported.

I verified in my lab, it's actually not support.

Would you please check and rectify?
